Resting

Resting is a micro MVC web framework that uses DBIx::Class and the
Template Toolkit.  See examples/ for examples, or "perldoc Resting"
for the manual.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Resting

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Resting

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Resting

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Resting

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Resting

